Product description

Bluetooth 5.4

No delay, low power consumption, widely compatible.

Stable connection with high-fidelity sound quality up to15 meters transmission distance.

Open Ear Design

Directional Audio Technology minimizes sound leakage, preserves privacy. Stay aware of your surroundings for enhanced safety during sports.

APTX Support

Supports APTX (lossless music) and APTX-LL (lossless music with ultra-low latency) formats, providing immersive music or audio experience.

HD Bluelight Blocking Lenses

Effectively blocks over 90% of high-energy violet-blue light waves with High-transparency lenses, protecting the eyes, reduce strain.

Specifications

Bluetooth Version Bluetooth 5.4, compatible with all of devices with Bluetooth
Waterproof IP54, Unfazed by Rain, Splashes, or Sweat
Lenses Anti Blue Light and Polarized HD Lenses
Battery 160 Milliamp Hours, 7 hours for continuous music or call, 10 days for standby
Technology Noise-canceling and Directional audio
Support Music Formats Supports APTX and APTX-LL
Number of Speakers 2
